<font size=2><table width="100%" bgcolor="#004b97"><font color=#d2d200><b>Baleen Plate Girdle</b></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=1><a style="color: #ffffff" href="mailto:jcsmith@amazinghideaways.com?subject=Regarding: Baleen Plate Girdle">Submit Info</a></font></table>
<font color=white>






<br><br>


<b>Inventory Slots:</b> Waist
<br>







<b>Armor Class:</b> 12<br>

<b>Size:</b> Medium<br>
<b>Weight:</b> 1<br>

<br>
<b>Classes:</b> WAR CLR PAL SHD BRD<br>
<b>Races:</b> HUM BAR ERU HEF VAH<br>




<br>

<b>Description:</b> <br>This item is sometimes dropped during the Cloak of Truth quest.<br><br>















<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Found On 

<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Arbogast%22">Arbogast</a></b></font></table><br>
<b>Level:</b> 44 - 44<br>
<b>Classification:</b> Quest_NPC<br>
<b>Sociality:</b> Social<br>

<img src="http://www.amazinghideaways.com/uploads/eqbestiary/Arbogast/picture/arbogast.jpg" align="right">









<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Obtained in 
<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqquestfull&eqquests.quest_name=%22Cloak%20of%20Truth%22">Cloak of Truth</a> Quest</b></font></table><br>
<b>Recommended Level:</b> 50<br>
<b>Starting NPC:</b> Arbogast<br><br>

<b>Description</b>:<br>
This is the quest for the Cloak of Truth, a very nice cloak, especially for casters because of the +5% meditate.<BR><BR>The spoiler is given in no nonsense format.<BR><BR>1) Ask Arbogast(in an Inn near bank of Katta Castellum), "what proof" and he will give you a vial of water.<BR><BR>2) Go to the second floor of the government building in Katta and give that vial to Phenic Dionicas. He will give you a silver wrapping(container).<BR><BR>3) Now you must bring a lockpicker and head to the castle in Katta. Behind a locked door on a table you wil find Nathyn's Memoirs. Grab them.<BR><BR>4) Combine them in to the silver wrapping and give the result to Arbogast.<BR><BR>5) Say, "what exodus" to Arbogast and he will give you a Gold Wrapping(container).<BR><BR>6) Head to Shadow Haven and kill Peqi Biato. He is in a building near hte casters guild, a level 45 wizard. He will drop a book.<BR><BR>7) Combine the book in to the Gold Wrapping and give the result to Arbogast in Katta Castellum. He will give you Black Paper.<BR><BR>8) Head to Akheva Ruins and kill the the Xi mobs until you get two Akuel Xi Ans Vius's. <BR><BR>The easiest way to get these is to kill The Protector(he is a patroller who patrols the Centi area, including near the entrance from time to time) as he drops it and is easy to get to. <BR><BR>Stay until you get two of them as they are No Rent.<BR><BR>9) Combine the two Akuel Xi Ans Vius in to the Black Paper and return the result to Arbogast, and bring a couple of friends.<BR><BR>10) After returning them Arbogast and Miller will head to the bank to get some items for you, then decide they don't want to give up the items. <BR><BR>You will need to kill them and loot the clasp and wrap from their corpses. You combine the clasp into the wrap to create the Cloak of Truth.<BR><BR>They also drop other items which may be useful to those helping you.<br>


<br><table width="300" bgcolor="#004b97"><b><font color=#d2d200>Found in <a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqzone&eqzones.zone_name=%22Katta%20Castellum%22">Katta Castellum</a></b></font></table><br>
<b>Continent:</b> Luclin<br>
<b>Zone Type:</b> Town<br>
<b>Level Ranges:</b> 1 - 60<br>
<b>Connects To:</b> Tenebrous Mountains, Twilight Sea<br><br>

<b>Description:</b><br>This city has Bard, Cleric, Druid, Enchanter, Magician, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, Shaman, Warrior and wizard guild halls.  It was built by the combine empire when they moved to Luclin.<br>




